race_granturismo_beta
INFOMap made by Biohazard.pt Yeah I am quite full of suprises.. I managed to finish two maps in about a week or so for the same mod. I hope you enjoy this one as much as the last one. This one was a bit easier yet there still were compile problems. Enjoy and have fun racing it. This map was created for the portuguese FRAGXL community.
MAP INFOType: Rally Race Players: 16 max. - Ambient sounds - HDR lightning - Simple track - Sunny weather - Real gran turismo track - 3 Laps
SCREENSHOT INFOScreenshot 1 - Start Zone Screenshot 2 - Map overview Screenshot 3 - One of the turns Screenshot 4 - Pit stop garages Screenshot 5 - Ready Zone Screenshot 6 - Spectator platforms
If you want to post this map on other forums go ahead but give me credit for my own map. Thanks go to Unreal. Please feel free to rate, stamp or/and post some feedback.
